content: wtfsayo: Extremely active contributor who merged 22 PRs this month, with significant work on the Generic Model Loading refactor (PR #3114, +78k/-103k lines) and several critical fixes for plugin build issues. Consistently worked on maintenance and cleanup tasks, including removing build files (PR #3117, removing 27k lines), fixing dependency issues across multiple plugins, and updating documentation (PR #2280, +2.3k/-697 lines). Demonstrated strong code review leadership with 330 reviews (256 approvals) while maintaining a steady work pattern, being active on 26 out of 31 days and focusing primarily on codebase maintenance and bug fixes.
